Key Match Events: Wyatt Langford hit a walk-off grand slam to lift the Texas Rangers to a 7-4 comeback win
Others: This was only the eighth time in regular season history that the Rangers have won with a walk-off grand slam, the first since Marlon Byrd on Aug. 4, 2008. Wyatt Langford is the first Rangers rookie to ever win a game with a walk-off grand slam.
